A '''High [[Prefect (Yuuzhan Vong rank)|Prefect]]''' was a high-ranking title in [[Yuuzhan Vong]] society. It signified the leader of the [[intendant caste]]. Notable High Prefects included [[Yoog Skell]] and [[Drathul]].

